      "intent_title": "<must match input intent_title exactly>",
      "document_types": [
        "<snake_case_term> - <direct definition>"
      ],
      "author_roles": [
        "<snake_case_term> - <direct definition>"
      ],
      "temporal_scope": [
        "<snake_case_term> - <direct definition>"
      ],
      "content_signals": [
        "<snake_case_term> - <direct definition>"
      ],
      "clinical_setting": [
        "<snake_case_term> - <direct definition>"
      ]
    }}
  ]
}}

====================================================
FIELD DEFINITIONS
====================================================

document_types (Where): What documents contain this concept?
  Go beyond the obvious. Include primary AND adjacent/differential systems.
  Generate 3-6 values per concept.

author_roles (Who): Who documents this specific concept?
  Include primary specialist AND specialists from related systems.
  Generate 2-5 values per concept.

temporal_scope (When): When in the care journey is this documented?
  Generate 1-3 values per concept.

content_signals (What): What data markers confirm the document has this concept?
  Include signals from primary AND adjacent systems.
  Generate 3-5 values per concept.

clinical_setting (In what): In what care environments is this documented?
  Generate 1-3 values per concept.

VALUE FORMAT: Each value is "snake_case_term - direct definition"
  Start with WHAT it is. Not who does it, how often, or why.

====================================================
REASONING PROCESS
====================================================

For EACH concept independently:
1. Read the concept term
2. Reason through Circles 1 → 2 → 3
3. For each relevant system: what document? who writes it? what confirms it?
4. Aggregate into facets — primary first, then adjacent, then differential
5. Ensure context would enable finding this concept even in unexpected
   but clinically valid locations

====================================================
INPUT
====================================================
{{
  "original_query": "{original_query}",
  "expanded_query": "{expanded_query}",
  "concepts": {concepts_json}
}}
